Dialogue: 3,0:21:37.99,0:21:39.78,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}喂喂　先等等
Dialogue: 3,0:21:39.99,0:21:42.16,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}太刺激的內容
Dialogue: 3,0:21:42.58,0:21:46.29,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}放到最後再說吧
Dialogue: 3,0:21:46.50,0:21:50.58,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}現實中滿是不如意
Dialogue: 3,0:21:50.92,0:21:55.21,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}那就都塞到瓶子裡
Dialogue: 3,0:21:55.80,0:21:58.34,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}準備好參加派對了嗎?
Dialogue: 3,0:21:58.34,0:22:00.34,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}不等你了哦
Dialogue: 3,0:22:00.88,0:22:04.39,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}另一個故事就要開始了
Dialogue: 3,0:22:05.10,0:22:07.27,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}無數氣泡呼呼冒出
Dialogue: 3,0:22:07.39,0:22:09.52,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}無數氣泡啵啵破裂
Dialogue: 3,0:22:09.77,0:22:13.11,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}生活就像汽水
Dialogue: 3,0:22:13.86,0:22:16.28,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}無論是爸爸媽媽的事
Dialogue: 3,0:22:16.40,0:22:18.57,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}還是悶在心底的回憶
Dialogue: 3,0:22:18.65,0:22:22.99,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}都會化作氣泡消失掉
Dialogue: 3,0:22:23.49,0:22:25.58,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}哭泣憂愁又煩惱
Dialogue: 3,0:22:25.78,0:22:27.79,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}無數往事多紛擾
Dialogue: 3,0:22:28.08,0:22:31.50,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}都沒關係的
Dialogue: 3,0:22:32.17,0:22:34.67,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}所有往事盡懷抱
Dialogue: 3,0:22:34.67,0:22:36.92,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}塞進瓶子使勁搖
Dialogue: 3,0:22:36.92,0:22:41.22,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}噗嗤全部釋放　大家一起歡笑
Dialogue: 3,0:22:41.30,0:22:44.47,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}咕嚕嚕　瞬間滿是氣泡
